New York photographer Justin Bettman designed and built a set for Jose Luis to propose to his girlfriend on Valentine's Day . 
  The set was built on the edge of the water in Williamsburg, where the couple had their first date  . 
  Bettman caught the media's attention when he began his 'Set in the Street' project in December . 
  Luis proposed on the set on the sidewalk where he and his girlfriend had first date . 
  Bettman built the set using furniture he found on Craigslist . 
 